"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"有無人睇過blue valentine"},{"pid":"649758bcce5afe8e2842bc4225d1c21a81b4b98e","tid":190142,"uid":91304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人睇過blue valentine</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3b0e7f810433fe74368ab1db6cb64b05a38ead","tid":190142,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩生花<br />\n畫面唔算好唯美果隻<br />\n反而有種隨手拈來唔造作魅力<br />\n睇完個心入面開朵花慢慢長大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘭花賊<br />\n唔知節奏算唔算慢... <br />\n又係睇完慢慢會發酵ge戲，好正</blockquote><br />\n兩生花真心正，當時我向戲院睇左三次。<br />\n<br />\n紅白藍三部曲都好正，我覺得奇斯洛夫斯基既戲拍得好靚，好有佢自已一套既美學同對哲理生命既探討，而三部曲入面佢好考妙利用一 d 場景將三套戲既角色既無關聯但又將串聯為三部曲完整主體。"},{"pid":"618fe1d24d5ff671b3735816fb97704e1f89da63","tid":190142,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241p8P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241p8P6.jpg&h=e3bc42a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得節奏未算話&quot;好&quot;慢，不過對冇睇開呢種類型嘅人可能會投入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你真係追求慢嘅可以睇下Paterson<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近安排睇左，以慢來講都算一絕"},{"pid":"fd28128f0e178fef3376afdccf377be5e38f6d6e","tid":190142,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"牯嶺街少年殺人事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37183839cbcdb4caa7b0272ada33658f14847f87","tid":190142,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>The man from earth</blockquote><br />\n呢套係文戲中無畫面 只係對話都做到節奏快既感覺 係結尾個講佢個女太老土</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢套我覺得未算慢，甚至覺得幾緊湊<br />\n不過的確係經典<img src=